default major retailers agreed to continue monitoring carrier bag u
defaultsage during 2010, 2011 and 2012,
default although no formal target was agreed to measure against. The participating retailers were: Asda (including ex-Netto stores), Co-operative Group, Marks &amp; Spencer, Morrison’s, Sainsbury’s
default, Tesco and Waitrose. WRAP continued with its
default role 
defaultof data collection, analysis and publication.
